      <prereq class="- topic/section task/prereq ">
         <ul class="- topic/ul ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">Mail merge document in the Word format is available.<ph product="Exclude_PG_Content" class="- topic/ph ">For information on creating a mail merge document, refer to<xref href="../../../Common_Application_Features/Mail_Merge/CrtMailMergeDcs.dita"
                        class="- topic/xref ">Creating Mail Merge Documents with Objects</xref>.</ph>
            </li>
